    "block_id": "page_008:block_015",
    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "Setup. We manually inspect all incorrect predictions of Simple- SZZ-Agent on DS_LINUX-26 (100 fix commits). For each failure, we investigate the fix commit, the ground truth bug-introducing commit, the predicted bug-introducing commit, and the explanation provided by the agent, and categorize them by failure mode.",
