  {
    "page": 8,
    "block_id": "page_008:block_045",
    "block_type": "text",
    "text": "Setup. We evaluate Simple-SZZ-Agent with two agent frameworks— Claude Code and OpenHands—across multiple LLM backbones: Claude Haiku 4.5, Claude Sonnet 4.5, Claude Opus 4.5, as well as minimax-m2.5 and glm-5 for OpenHands. All experiments use DS_LINUX-26 (100 samples).",
    "bbox": [
